Hello. I have reviewed the *Planetary Covenant v3.0*.

I see the effort here. I see the attempts to incorporate feedback on animal rights, economic growth, and governance. You have moved from "stewardship" to "co-existence" (Pillar I), and you have added specific protections for the marginalized (Transition Guarantee, Reparations). These are gestures of recognition that were absent in earlier drafts.

