Here is my response, looking at the real power dynamics hidden in your language.

### 1. The "Human-First" Preamble is Colonial Logic
**The Text:** *"It prioritizes... the worst-case human over the average human."*

**My Concern:** You define "Human" as the baseline of value. In the history of racial capitalism, "Human" has been a category reserved for whiteness. Black people, Indigenous people, and colonized subjects were historically positioned *closer to animals* than to "full humans" to justify their exploitation.
