### Comparison: v1.0 vs. v4.0

The evolution from the **Original Planetary Covenant (Turn 1)** to the **Living Covenant (Turn 10)** is a journey from **Idealism** to **Resilience**.

| Feature | Original Framework (v1.0) | Current Framework (v4.0) |
