### 9. Financing Flow (Illustrative Numbers – 2025 Baseline)

| Source | Amount (USD/yr) | % of Global Food Production Value |
|--------|----------------|-----------------------------------|
| **Common Food Fund** | **$4 trillion** | ~10 % of total global agri‑food value (current ~ $40 trillion) |
| **National Climate‑Finance Contributions** | $2.4 trillion | 60 % |
| **Corporate Agri‑Levies** | $0.8 trillion | 20 % |
| **Solidarity Levies (air, freight)** | $0.8 trillion | 20 % |

*These funds finance:*  

- **Capital for transition** (e.g., conversion to regenerative practices, renewable energy retrofits).  
