## TL;DR – The Blueprint in One Sentence  

> **A globally coordinated, open‑source network of community‑owned food hubs that produce regenerative, climate‑smart agro‑ecosystems, financed by a transparent Common Food Fund, and governed by the people who farm, eat, and steward the land—delivering enough nutritious food for all while restoring the planet.**

