### 1. What the New Pillar 9 Looks Like (in practice)

> **Pillar 9 – Strategic‑Resource Sovereignty & Tech‑Equity**  
> *Goal:* Ensure that no single state, corporation, or supranational body can monopolise the technologies or inputs that are essential for planetary survival.  

- **Critical Inputs**: (i) high‑density energy storage materials (e.g., lithium, cobalt, solid‑state battery electrolytes), (ii) high‑density data‑centres, (ii) synthetic‑biology enzymes, (iii) advanced AI compute clusters.  
